# Experiments directory
# 
# Each training run creates a subdirectory here, e.g.:
#
#   experiments/
#   ├── dqn_run/
#   │   ├── train_log.csv
#   │   ├── checkpoint_best.pt
#   │   ├── checkpoint_ep500.pt
#   │   └── checkpoint_final.pt
#   └── qlearning_run/
#       ├── train_log.csv
#       ├── checkpoint_best.pkl
#       └── checkpoint_final.pkl
#
# Controlled by TrainConfig.experiment_dir in configs/config.py
# or by --exp flag on run_train.py
